headline: This High-Yield Stock Is My Worst-Performing Investment and I Still Love It
summary: When I look at my brokerage account, there is one stock that stands out as particularly disappointing performance-wise: Hormel Foods (NYSE: HRL).  Here's why I still love Hormel despite the fact that it is my worst performer.  Hormel, specifically, owns the No. 1 or No. 2 brands in 40 retail categories.
